What is it?

6
00:02:27,036 --> 00:02:30,949
Being able to be together
with you like this is great.

7
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:34,375
I feel a little over my head with ecstasy.

8
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,669
Don't you feel that it is a little strange?

9
00:02:37,762 --> 00:02:40,092
