so I just said it.

16
00:03:07,196 --> 00:03:11,837
Next time, I will not just suppress it.
I will say whatever I feel.

17
00:03:13,843 --> 00:03:15,804
I missed you very much.

18
00:03:16,621 --> 00:03:18,332
I missed you,

19
00:03:18,566 --> 00:03:20,385
