20
00:03:30,379 --> 00:03:32,139
Hyung Tae.

21
00:03:33,458 --> 00:03:37,043
My essay wasn't chosen again.

22
00:03:37,776 --> 00:03:39,763
It's alright.

23
00:03:39,956 --> 00:03:43,235
Player Kim Joo Hwan hit a home run.

24
00:03:43,428 --> 00:03:44,628
I saw that too.

25
00:03:44,678 --> 00:03:45,962
Do you think he was very suave there?

26
00:03:46,051 --> 00:03:50,190
I went to look for you to tell you the news,
but you weren't home.

27
00:03:52,314 --> 00:03:53,806
You went to my house?

28
00:03:54,003 --> 00:03:56,851
