The whole day I was looking
for you everywhere.

30
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:17,182
Nan Hee.

31
00:04:22,844 --> 00:04:27,781
I now completely understand my heart.

32
00:04:39,147 --> 00:04:40,529
Say it.

33
00:04:43,364 --> 00:04:44,643
I love you.

34
00:04:46,401 --> 00:04:49,167
So mushy.

35
00:04:52,491 --> 00:04:54,189
I...

36
00:04:55,297 --> 00:04:58,438
Only when it was all the way up here,
I was able to say it.

37
00:04:59,644 --> 00:05:01,923
But you had a heavy heart, right?

38
00:05:02,219 --> 00:05:04,946
Don't make wild guesses.

39
00:05:09,311 --> 00:05:11,784
From now, I want to believe.

40
00:05:12,534 --> 00:05:14,559
The Oppa's lies.

41
00:05:19,032 --> 00:05:20,849
Come in.

42
