I know what the feeling of Sung Ah is like now.

43
00:05:40,011 --> 00:05:42,174
All this is all my fault.

44
00:05:42,401 --> 00:05:45,075
I am already so old,
yet I still fought with people.

45
00:05:45,341 --> 00:05:46,892
Fought?

46
00:05:49,095 --> 00:05:51,063
