47
00:05:54,362 --> 00:05:55,951
With Jun Mo.

48
00:05:56,494 --> 00:05:57,995
Exchanged heavy blows?

49
00:06:00,152 --> 00:06:02,958
Did Jun Mo really hit you?

50
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:05,678
Did you instruct him to do that?

51
00:06:05,994 --> 00:06:08,621
Would I get beaten up by Sung Ah too?

52
00:06:10,311 --> 00:06:12,664
Looks like love, there can only be one.

53
00:06:12,733 --> 00:06:13,543
One?

54
00:06:16,915 --> 00:06:19,464
