what would my life become?

67
00:07:13,871 --> 00:07:15,955
What's wrong?

68
00:07:18,064 --> 00:07:19,546
I don't know.

69
00:07:20,672 --> 00:07:24,874
These words sound better than I love you.

70
00:07:27,787 --> 00:07:30,522
