74
00:07:37,427 --> 00:07:38,454
Oh.

75
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:42,974
If I faint off halfway while talking,
don't be alarmed.

76
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:45,322
Then lie down.

77
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,406
I want to stay like this.

78
00:07:47,781 --> 00:07:51,286
Be careful, you might catch the cold from me.

79
00:07:53,916 --> 00:07:58,747
Us... next time, we aren't friends anymore, right?

80
00:08:00,996 --> 00:08:04,295
I have failed in love with a lot of guys.

81
00:08:05,193 --> 00:08:07,435
But those words hurt me the most.

82
