95
00:09:07,566 --> 00:09:11,927
And I am very thankful that
I can understand how you feel.

96
00:09:12,236 --> 00:09:14,551
I want to talk to you,

97
00:09:14,705 --> 00:09:18,872
use up all my remaining energy,
then have a good sleep.

98
00:09:19,123 --> 00:09:21,675
Tomorrow is the weekend.

99
00:09:22,331 --> 00:09:23,894
Okay.

100
00:09:26,383 --> 00:09:28,351
