104
00:10:15,882 --> 00:10:17,734
Give it.

105
00:10:20,281 --> 00:10:22,403
The weather is so good.

106
00:10:28,841 --> 00:10:32,391
Hey, you hugged it the whole night,
one whole night.

107
00:10:32,488 --> 00:10:35,690
What's so great about that guitar
to be holding so tightly onto it?

108
00:10:35,998 --> 00:10:39,258
Even if you spent the whole night playing the guitar,
Seung Won's standard will still be better than yours.

109
00:10:39,335 --> 00:10:41,207
