110
00:10:41,303 --> 00:10:43,792
Looks like you are more interested
in guitar than your major.

111
00:10:43,869 --> 00:10:44,969
Which direction are you going
to pursue your career in?

112
00:10:45,046 --> 00:10:47,130
Such a good thing,
why should it become a career?

113
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,679
I will only fall in love with the guitar.

114
00:10:49,737 --> 00:10:50,644
What?

115
00:10:50,702 --> 00:10:53,017
