118
00:10:57,975 --> 00:10:59,501
What's yours?

119
00:10:59,906 --> 00:11:02,125
I have three dreams.

120
00:11:05,463 --> 00:11:08,800
I will live a little longer before deciding.

121
00:11:10,468 --> 00:11:15,522
