separation has a huge effect on you.

141
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:33,585
So there were some things I didn't dare do.

142
00:13:36,479 --> 00:13:38,910
Wasn't able to enjoy thoroughly together.

143
00:13:39,508 --> 00:13:41,265
Sung Ah.

144
00:13:43,233 --> 00:13:47,651
