145
00:13:50,892 --> 00:13:53,808
Hence I asked you to stay.

146
00:13:56,760 --> 00:14:02,390
But now, I don't know what I can do for you.

147
00:14:05,882 --> 00:14:08,641
For this, I am sorry.

148
00:14:23,932 --> 00:14:31,239
<i>As time goes by, we meet new people</i>

149
00:14:32,342 --> 00:14:44,507
<i>Everyone says that it will be
forgotten and become indifferent</i>

150
00:14:44,565 --> 00:14:48,458
<i>The tears doesn't stop</i>

151
00:14:48,535 --> 00:14:53,174
<i>But the time stops and doesn't go</i>

152
