<i>You say you are very happy</i>

153
00:15:01,891 --> 00:15:08,141
<i>Letting me go, but you are
smiling and saying thank you</i>

154
00:15:08,271 --> 00:15:15,410
<i>You are afraid that saying
you loved me will hurt me</i>

155
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:18,896
<i>Only saying thank you</i>

156
00:15:18,973 --> 00:15:22,667
<i>Wishing that I meet a better person</i>

157
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:27,901
<i>Stay, I am not in time to say</i>

158
00:15:28,036 --> 00:15:32,261
<i>I wasn't in time to get near to you</i>

159
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:39,041
<i>I always get choked up and can't say a thing</i>

160
00:15:39,104 --> 00:15:42,861
<i>Thinking of you so much I can't breath</i>

161
00:15:42,952 --> 00:15:47,042
