180
00:18:39,193 --> 00:18:40,455
I am much better.

181
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:43,399
Looks like the cold is better.

182
00:18:43,478 --> 00:18:45,098
That is good.

183
00:18:48,371 --> 00:18:54,089
