203
00:19:41,005 --> 00:19:45,796
<i>{\a6}But someday a good day will come to me too</i>

204
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:43,427
You…

205
00:19:45,857 --> 00:19:47,062
Me too.

206
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:48,333
<i>{\a6}This is the beginning</i>

207
00:19:48,393 --> 00:19:52,427
<i>The star of life is me</i>

208
00:19:52,575 --> 00:19:58,584
<i>Don't forget, who you are</i>

209
00:20:00,543 --> 00:20:01,472
Go on up.

210
00:20:01,709 --> 00:20:03,338
Call me.

211
00:20:04,809 --> 00:20:06,064
Go on.

212
00:20:09,246 --> 00:20:12,697
<i>It's okay, don't worry</i>

213
00:20:13,027 --> 00:20:16,678
<i>It's suppose to be hard for everyone</i>

214
00:20:16,784 --> 00:20:20,210
<i>After one night's sleep</i>

215
00:20:20,524 --> 00:20:23,778
<i>Everything will be fine again</i>

216
00:20:24,042 --> 00:20:27,480
<i>{\a6}I don't know how to give up</i>

217
00:20:25,748 --> 00:20:27,514
<i>The room is the same as yesterday,</i>

218
00:20:27,548 --> 00:20:29,395
<i>but I don't feel lonely anymore.</i>

219
00:20:28,517 --> 00:20:31,775
<i>{\a6}I'm fine and strong</i>

220
00:20:31,792 --> 00:20:35,314
<i>Always cheerful and happy</i>

221
00:20:35,739 --> 00:20:39,035
<i>I will patiently endure it</i>

222
00:20:39,254 --> 00:20:40,132
<i>I believe</i>

223
00:20:40,161 --> 00:20:41,852
<i>Even though living is hard</i>

224
00:20:41,870 --> 00:20:44,097
<i>Those empty spots that family can fill in,</i>

225
00:20:41,889 --> 00:20:43,932
<i>{\a6}Even if I fall in love</i>

226
00:20:43,989 --> 00:20:47,574
<i>{\a6}I will never cry or complain</i>

227
